# VS Code REST Client 或类似工具可直接运行以下示例

### 请求验证码（有效手机号）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/request-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 请求验证码（无效手机号）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/request-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "123"
}

### 登录（成功示例——请确保先请求验证码并使用正确的6位code）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "code": "123456"
}

### 登录（未注册手机号）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13100000000",
  "code": "123456"
}

### 登录（验证码错误）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "code": "000000"
}